OL,3,CDangerous culture of accepting drugs
OL,4,Ccrisis in prisons must be broken, MPs
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FSome 39% of prisoners find it easy to
OL,8,Fget drugs ` and the use and trade of
OL,9,Fdrugs are crippling the HM Prisons and
OL,10,FProbation Service's (HMPPS) ability to
OL,11,Fkeep control and rehabilitate
OL,12,Foffenders, according to the Justice
OL,13,FCommittee.
OL,15,FA report published on Friday warned of
OL,16,Fthe "unacceptable" human cost from the
OL,17,Fcrisis, with 16% of 833 deaths
OL,18,Finvestigated between December 2022 to
OL,19,F2024 being determined as drugs-related
OL,20,Fby the prisons ombudsman.
