OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FMPs heard that inmates in debt were
OL,8,Fbeing forced to test new drugs,
OL,9,Fsometimes for the entertainment of
OL,10,Fother prisoners, while staff becoming
OL,11,Fdesensitised to daily suffering was a
OL,12,Fsign of a "failed system".
OL,14,FThe report found 11% of men and 19% of
OL,15,Fwomen said they had developed a
OL,16,Fproblem with drugs, alcohol or non-
OL,17,Fprescription medication since arriving
OL,18,Fin prison.
