OL,15,FSlaughter, said: "The committee's
OL,16,Ffindings during this inquiry were
OL,17,Fsobering: put simply the drugs crisis
OL,18,Facross the prison system has reached
OL,19,F'endemic' levels, fostering a
OL,20,F'dangerous culture of acceptance that
OL,21,Fmust be broken'.
